---
title: Three-Cheese Agnolotti Gratin with Kale, Tomato and Basil Pesto
description: Believe it—this one-pot wonder will have a delicious oven-baked pasta on the table in 30 minutes. Simmering agnolotti in its own tomato sauce is the time-saving trick to this recipe. The best part? That crispy, cheesy topping.
